---
export const prerender = true;
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About MOSION — The Cinema Africa Deserves"
  description="MOSION is mobile cinema for African film. Learn the story behind the platform - why it was built, what it solves, and where it's going."
  canonical="https://mosion.app/about"
  ogTitle="MOSION - About"
  ogDescription="A ₦15.6 billion market. 122 cinemas. 230 million people. The infrastructure was always missing - until now."
  logoOnly={true}
  css={["/about.css"]}
>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-grain"></div>
    <div class="hero-accent-line"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        The cinema<br />
        <em>Africa deserves.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        A &#8358;15.6 billion market. 122 cinemas. 230 million people. The
        infrastructure was always missing - until now.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-bottom">
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-num">&#8358;15.6B</span>
        <span class="hero-stat-label">Box office. 3 cities. 230M people.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="hero-stat hero-stat-delay-2">
        <span class="hero-stat-num">98.8%</span>
        <span class="hero-stat-label">Of Nigeria with no cinema access.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="hero-stat hero-stat-delay-3">
        <span class="hero-stat-num">1</span>
        <span class="hero-stat-label">Platform solving it.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="story reveal">
    <p class="story-label">The Story</p>
    <h2 class="story-headline">
      Why MOSION<br />
      <em>exists.</em>
    </h2>

    <div class="pull-quote">
      <p>
        "African cinema is producing world-class content. The infrastructure to
        distribute it was never built."
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="story-body">
      Nigeria's box office grossed <strong>&#8358;15.6 billion in 2025</strong>
      - a record year, with Nollywood claiming more than half the market for the
      first time in history. The demand for African cinema is real, growing, and
      impossible to ignore.
    </p>

    <p class="story-body">
      But that entire &#8358;15.6 billion passed through just
      <strong>122 cinemas</strong>, almost all in Lagos, Abuja, and Port
      Harcourt. A filmmaker in Enugu premieres nationally - and reaches 1.2% of
      the country. A viewer in Ilorin wants to watch opening weekend - and has no
      option.
    </p>

    <p class="story-body">
      MOSION is the answer to that gap. Not a streaming service. Not a
      subscription platform. A <strong>mobile cinema</strong> - pay-per-view,
      premiere-first, built for the device already in 230 million pockets. The
      model is cinema's own model. The delivery is the infrastructure cinema
      never had.
    </p>

    <p class="story-body">
      And for filmmakers, MOSION Studio is being built to provide something
      traditional distribution has always withheld:
      <strong>full financial visibility</strong>. Approved partners will manage
      releases, review title performance, and handle payouts through one
      controlled workflow.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="vision reveal">
    <p class="vision-label">The Vision</p>
    <h2 class="vision-statement">
      "We're building cinema<br />
      that lives in <em>your pocket.</em>"
    </h2>

    <div class="vision-pillars">
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Access Without Infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="pillar-body">
          A cinema only works where a building exists. MOSION doesn't need one.
          Approved filmmakers, distributors, and rights holders can premiere
          nationally. Any viewer - regardless of city or commute - can attend
          opening weekend.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Transparency for Creators</h3>
        <p class="pillar-body">
          Filmmakers have been the last to know what their own films earned.
          MOSION Studio is designed to give approved partners a dedicated
          reporting dashboard, payout controls, and the financial clarity the
          industry has always withheld.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">The Cinema Model, Extended</h3>
        <p class="pillar-body">
          MOSION doesn't reinvent cinema economics. It extends them. The same
          60/40 revenue splits. The same premiere window. The same
          quality standard. Just delivered to where Africa actually watches.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="building reveal">
    <div class="building-left">
      <p class="story-label">Currently Building</p>
      <h2>
        <em>Founder-led.</em><br />
        Actively growing.
      </h2>
      <p>
        MOSION is currently built and led by its founder. We are actively
        looking to bring on a business-focused co-founder or key hire in
        filmmaker partnerships and sales as part of our seed raise.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are a filmmaker, distributor, investor, or operator who believes
        in what we're building - we'd like to talk.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:partners@mosion.app" class="building-cta">
        Get in touch &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="open-roles">
      <div class="role-row">
        <div class="role-info">
          <div class="role-title">Filmmaker Partnerships Lead</div>
          <div class="role-sub">Business Development &middot; Content Acquisition</div>
        </div>
        <span class="role-status status-open">Open</span>
      </div>
      <div class="role-row">
        <div class="role-info">
          <div class="role-title">Customer Support Lead</div>
          <div class="role-sub">Support Systems &middot; Automation</div>
        </div>
        <span class="role-status status-progress">In Progress</span>
      </div>
      <div class="role-row">
        <div class="role-info">
          <div class="role-title">Co-Founder (Business)</div>
          <div class="role-sub">Operations &middot; Partnerships &middot; Growth</div>
        </div>
        <span class="role-status status-open">Open</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Fragment slot="scripts">
    <script is:inline src="/scripts/about.js" defer></script>
  </Fragment>
</MainLayout>
